subject: Golf
lead_paragraph: Nicole Castrale's string of birdies on the closing holes helped her post a career-low 64 at the McDonald's L.P.G.A. Championship in Havre de Grace, Md. She has a two-shot lead over Cristie Kerr and Pat Hurst.
